HEADWORD: Epistilbite
<hw>Ep`i*stil"bite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>epi-</ets> + <ets>stilbite</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A
